{"title":"望雁","authors":["程步涛"],"dates":[{"year":1997,"month":6,"day":24}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"望雁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"程步涛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"许久许久了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"仰望南天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是为了一只归雁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只咫尺天涯"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"已飞翔了一个百年"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"起风时"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"惦念她的翅膀不要折断"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来雨时"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"担心她无奈了栖在泥滩"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"终于"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她的毛羽如霞如锦"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"闪烁着一片灿烂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她的鸣叫清脆又嘹亮"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"使每一朵云彩都绽开笑脸"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"于是"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又在菊黄时"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又在秋熟时"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"数叨着哪天月亏"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哪天月满"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如今"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"月就要圆"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"月就要满"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春华已成为秋实"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"使每一个枝头都沉沉甸甸"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而长空"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那年年北归年年南飞的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"排成人字的雁阵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就要飞过长江"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飞过黄河"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飞过古长城饱经沧桑的一个个垛口"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飞过塞内塞外存留了几千年的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"汉瓦秦砖丝帛竹简"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那只飞了一个百年的大雁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"将第一次排在这雁阵里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"感受万里神州"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"腾起的滚滚热流"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"回忆古来难全的离合悲欢"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"古来难全"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"离合悲欢"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从现在起从今天起"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"真正成为宋词里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一缕缭人的轻烟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从现在起从今天起"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只愿金瓯不缺"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只愿明月常满"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"望雁是一种怀念"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"珍藏在一个民族的心间"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"秋来时我们望雁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"秋来时我们望雁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（作者单位：解放军文艺出版社）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":12,"page_end":12}